commit.title: A structure for installation of coqide.keys.
commit.message:
A structure for installation of coqide.keys.

We support specific default configuration files for MacOSX, Win32, and
other architectures (to be possibly refined further).

We do the installation in two steps:
- First we build a default file ide/coqide.keys for the corresponding
  architecture.
- Second, if not in local mode, we install the in CONFIGDIR at
  installation time.
In particular, this works also in local mode since the local mode
expects the default accel map to precisely be ide/coqide.keys.
